<text id="02-output-contract" title="Team Development Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema (draft-07) for the `TeamDevelopmentReport` produced by this methodology. Validator enforces required keys, per-field constraints, and forbidden patterns.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/team-development-report.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["team_id", "as_of", "tuckman_stage", "tuckman_confidence", "tuckman_evidence", "charter", "skills_gap_plan", "themes"],
  "properties": {
    "team_id": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1},
    "as_of": {"type": "string", "format": "date"},
    "tuckman_stage": {"enum": ["Forming", "Storming", "Norming", "Performing", "Adjourning"]},
    "tuckman_confidence": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0.0, "maximum": 1.0},
    "tuckman_evidence": {"type": "array", "minItems": 2, "items": {"type": "string"}},
    "charter": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["co_authored", "mission", "working_agreements"],
      "properties": {
        "co_authored": {"type": "boolean"},
        "mission": {"type": "string", "minLength": 10},
        "working_agreements": {"type": "array", "minItems": 3, "items": {"type": "string"}}
      }
    },
    "skills_gap_plan": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["skill", "gap_severity", "gap_options_evaluated", "chosen_option", "owner_role", "deadline_sprint"],
        "properties": {
          "skill": {"type": "string"},
          "gap_severity": {"enum": ["low", "medium", "high"]},
          "gap_options_evaluated": {"type": "array", "minItems": 4, "maxItems": 4, "items": {"enum": ["training", "pairing", "contracting", "hiring"]}},
          "chosen_option": {"enum": ["training", "pairing", "contracting", "hiring"]},
          "owner_role": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1},
          "deadline_sprint": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^S[0-9]+$"}
        }
      }
    },
    "themes": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["theme", "evidence_sprints", "proposed_experiment"],
        "properties": {
          "theme": {"type": "string"},
          "evidence_sprints": {"type": "array", "minItems": 2, "items": {"type": "string"}},
          "proposed_experiment": {"type": "string"}
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item>Any string field containing first/last names (regex `\b[A-Z][a-z]+\b\s+[A-Z][a-z]+\b` outside roles) — violates `no-individual-naming`.</item>
      <item>`tuckman_evidence` shorter than 2 entries — violates `tuckman-confidence-score`.</item>
      <item>`theme.evidence_sprints` shorter than 2 entries — violates `pattern-needs-two-sprints`.</item>
      <item>`skills_gap_plan.gap_options_evaluated` missing `training` or `pairing` — violates `training-before-hire`.</item>
      <item>`charter.co_authored: true` without a session record reference — violates `charter-co-authored`.</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "team_id": "checkout-squad",
  "as_of": "2026-05-23",
  "tuckman_stage": "Storming",
  "tuckman_confidence": 0.72,
  "tuckman_evidence": ["throughput dropped 28% over 2 sprints", "PR review conflict cited in 3 retros", "1:1 reports note role overlap"],
  "charter": {"co_authored": false, "mission": "Ship checkout to <2s p95 by Q3", "working_agreements": ["PR review SLA 24h", "async-first comms", "decisions via RFC"]},
  "skills_gap_plan": [
    {"skill": "loadtesting", "gap_severity": "high", "gap_options_evaluated": ["training", "pairing", "contracting", "hiring"], "chosen_option": "pairing", "owner_role": "SRE lead", "deadline_sprint": "S14"}
  ],
  "themes": [
    {"theme": "PR review backlog blocking merges", "evidence_sprints": ["S11", "S12", "S13"], "proposed_experiment": "Rotate review-day owner; cap WIP at 5"}
  ]
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "team_id": "checkout-squad",
  "as_of": "2026-05-23",
  "tuckman_stage": "Performing",
  "tuckman_confidence": 0.4,
  "tuckman_evidence": ["vibes"],
  "charter": {"co_authored": true, "mission": "Ship", "working_agreements": ["be good"]},
  "skills_gap_plan": [{"skill": "loadtesting", "gap_severity": "high", "gap_options_evaluated": ["hiring"], "chosen_option": "hiring", "owner_role": "PM", "deadline_sprint": "next"}],
  "themes": [{"theme": "Alice raised concern", "evidence_sprints": ["S13"], "proposed_experiment": "..."}]
}
]]></code>
    <note>Evidence too thin; charter co_authored without proof; hiring without training/pairing evaluation; single-sprint theme; individual name "Alice"; deadline_sprint not S-pattern.</note>
  </example>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-team-development.py">Validator script</reference>
</text>
